To all the clowns saying that Seattle is always rainy and never sees the sun: Seattle has *less* precipitation than NYC, Boston, Atlanta, Miami, New Orleans, etc... in fact it rains less in Seattle than on the Northern California coast. https://t.co/73n8zaLuwH

